        <num>CC 3302</num>
        <heading>3302.  Property burdened by judicial and legal mortgages</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3302.  Property burdened by judicial and legal mortgages
Judicial and legal mortgages burden all the property of the obligor that is made susceptible of mortgage by Paragraphs 1 through 4 of Article 3286 or that is expressly made subject to judicial or legal mortgage by other law.</p>
        </content>
